PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister of Supply and Services of GLEN G. McDOUGALL, of Sydney, Nova Scotia, as a director of the Board of Directors of the Canada Post Corporation to hold office during pleasure for a term of three years, in the place of the Honourable Stuart Douglas Boland Smith, Q.C., whose term has expired.
